    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's example, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain features the desirable ZF 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain remains precise up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The suspension geometry is tight, benefiting from reinforced subframe mounting points and refreshed dampers. A mechanically honest performance machine ready for the open road.",
