      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior boasts a vibrant finish that still catches the light, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with responsible highway driving. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has benefited from a strict adherence to its maintenance schedule; I have the full service records available for your peace of mind. The interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, featuring premium upholstery with no tears and an electronics suite where every button and feature functions as intended. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes are firm and responsive. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that balances performance with aesthetic appeal, this car is ready for the road.",
