      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six. The powertrain features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers sharp throttle response across the powerband. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring structural and internal longevity. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers, offering the precise feedback expected from an M-division chassis. A well-sorted enthusiast's choice for those prioritizing performance over a museum-grade finish.",
